  "text": "Commercially available kits (both from Amersham Biosciences, Buckinghamshire, UK) were used to determine 6-keto-prostaglandin (PG) F 1␣ (6-Keto-PGF 1␣ ) levels in cell supernatants and intracellular cAMP levels in cells treated with 3-isobutyl-1-methylxanthine (30 mol/L, 30 minutes) as described. [CITATION_1] ",
